('DA SPOT', '445 ALBEE SQUARE WEST, BROOKLYN, NY 11201', '347-903-6729', 2017, true, true, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2019/0047/files/Screenshot_2020-02-09-09-21-57_2_480x480.png?v=1586087614', 'boutique', 'https://daspotnyc.com/', 'Established in May 2017 by three independent Black creatives, Da Spot NYC ("DA SPOT") is a unique fashion boutique featuring 25+ creative brands by people of color. "DA SPOT" is also home to C.A.N.V.A.S Art Gallery, which features the works of local artists.'),
('Divine Express Catering', '992 Atlantic Ave, Brooklyn, NY 11238', '718-208-4488', 2005, true, true, 'https://scontent-lga3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/302099304_979039209714265_6756093443916564037_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=09cbfe&_nc_ohc=1IIGW4beaWQAX8cLx5h&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.xx&oh=00_AfDgsW-hfZ3Nk8oBUA6EjRdLPWt31Zv-j9lXUaKknzPF-Q&oe=645CB4B3', 'restaurant', 'https://dexpresscatering.com/', 'A family-owned and operated business specializing in Nigerian and African cuisine.'),
('Brooklyn Suya', '717 FRANKLIN AVE BROOKLYN, NY 11238', '718-513-0122', 2019, true, true, 'https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/08/07/dining/01HUNGRY-SUYA-slide-GTRT/01HUNGRY-SUYA-slide-GTRT-articleLarge.jpg?quality=75&auto=webp&disable=upscale', 'restaurant', 'https://www.brooklynsuya.com/', 'Brooklyn Suya represents a merging of the Brooklyn + Nigerian culture centered around what we call a Suya Bowl. Each bowl starts with rice topped with your choice of grilled protein, sides, cucumber, tomatoes, signature house sauces, and of course, your choice of  mild, medium, spicy suya mix or, if your brave enough, atomic suya spice.'),
('MADE BY MALYIA', '', '347-258-3108', 2014, true, false, 'https://scontent-lga3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/317998489_842782797036018_8852338841211053298_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=730e14&_nc_ohc=h5kZDnCEsZ0AX9_wLCa&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.xx&oh=00_AfDgbGkw0lIYnutLvGMwMhipCu5uJceVKBJqyRPFnQzqrw&oe=645CD7CD', 'jewelry', 'https://madebymalyia.com/', 'Each piece of jewelry from Made by Malyia is familiar yet unexpected, focusing on natural influences to give movement to the lines within the designs. The visionary behind the brand, Malyia, pulls inspiration from nature, travel, African culture, architecture and more to fuse each of these touch points into an innovative piece. All pieces are utterly versatile, using ethically sourced materials.'),
('Aseem Tri8e', '', '', 2020, true, false, 'https://scontent-lga3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/277001484_108116935180554_6280968332157799816_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=09cbfe&_nc_ohc=r5K4WyKhucgAX-6lLq6&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.xx&oh=00_AfC8meXY-M8pUcT-D5k3BMohHxqC55W4kYQcO-R4XioJdw&oe=645C02B7', 'boutique', 'https://aseemtri8e.com/', 'Aseem means "unlimited/limitless/infinite" I feel it best describes the positive movement my friend Jace and I established. Sharing with others the power to unleash their LIMITLESS potential in all they seek to do. I was inspired by my family, unity with my soul tribe, and the divine forces of the universe to put together something special and meaningful that we all can enjoy!'),
